OL,3,CUnhealthy food costs UK more than
OL,4,C#260bn per year, report says
OL,6,FThe health impacts of the UK's
OL,7,Funhealthy food system is costing an
OL,8,Festimated #268 billion every year, a
OL,9,Freport claims.
OL,11,FThe Food Farming and Countryside
OL,12,FCommission (FFCC) calculated the
OL,13,Fdirect and indirect impact of diet-
OL,14,Frelated ill health by combining the
OL,15,Fcost of healthcare, social care,
OL,16,Fwelfare spending, productivity losses
OL,17,Fand identifying what proportion
OL,18,Frelates to food.
