OL,3,CUnhealthy food costs UK more than
OL,4,C#260bn per year, report says
OL,6,FIt found food-related costs of #67.5
OL,7,Fbillion in healthcare, #14.3 billion
OL,8,Fin social care, #10.1 billion in
OL,9,Fwelfare, productivity losses of #116.4
OL,10,Fbillion and #60 billion that can be
OL,11,Flinked to the chronic disease
OL,12,Fattributable to the current food
OL,13,Fecosystem, the research states.
OL,15,FProfessor Tim Jackson, who carried out
OL,16,Fthe analysis at Surrey University,
OL,17,Fsaid: "The connection between diet and
OL,18,Fhealth is often discussed, but the
OL,19,Feconomics of that link are staggering.
