OL,3,CUnhealthy food costs UK more than
OL,4,C#260bn per year, report says
OL,6,FUltra-processed foods constitute over
OL,7,Fhalf of the UK adult diet and almost
OL,8,Ftwo thirds of the adolescent diet and
OL,9,Fthe market, which has rapidly grown
OL,10,Fover the last two decades, is set to
OL,11,Fincrease in the coming year, the FFCC
OL,12,Fstates.
OL,14,FThe report says the right to healthy
OL,15,Ffood should be enshrined in law, there
OL,16,Fshould be regulation of the food
OL,17,Fenvironment to prevent harm and money
OL,18,Fcould be redirected towards a
OL,19,Fhealthier, greener, fairer and more
OL,20,Fresilient new food economy.
