OL,3,CUnhealthy food costs UK more than
OL,4,C#260bn per year, report says
OL,6,FFFCC chief executive Sue Pritchard
OL,7,Fsuggested "there is a clear and urgent
OL,8,Feconomic case for changing the UK food
OL,9,Fsystem".
OL,11,FShe added: "The state of the nation's
OL,12,Fhealth is not simply the result of
OL,13,Funder-investment in the NHS. It
OL,14,Frepresents the longstanding failure to
OL,15,Ftake seriously the critical
OL,16,Frelationship between food and farming,
OL,17,Fhealth and inequalities."
