OL,3,CUnhealthy food costs UK more than
OL,4,C#260bn per year, report says
OL,6,FEarlier this week, the Food
OL,7,FFoundation's annual State of the
OL,8,FNation's Food Industry report
OL,9,Fsuggested the UK food system is
OL,10,F"relentlessly" pushing consumers to
OL,11,Fmake unhealthy choices.
OL,13,FIn September, the Government confirmed
OL,14,Fthat a ban on junk food adverts being
OL,15,Fshown on TV before 9pm will come into
OL,16,Fforce on October 1 next year, although
OL,17,Fthere are already well-established
OL,18,Frestrictions that prohibit such ads
OL,19,Ffrom appearing on dedicated children's
OL,20,Fchannels or around children's
OL,21,Fprogrammes.
